{"tid":2331250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12名囚犯於中國遭受酷刑的經歷","createTime":"2020-12-18T15:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T15:41:37.000Z","uid":161603,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a440cb8baedc16c8fee753c7abd74c06c8b4dc","tid":2331250,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"杜斌長年研究歷史及關注弱勢群體，2013年其拍攝的紀錄片《小鬼頭上的女人》在香港上映時向《蘋果日報》表示，長約100分鐘的《小鬼頭上的女人》紀錄了遼寧馬三家女子勞教所12名女囚遭受酷刑的經歷，包括女獄警毆打上訪者、被綁在死人床三個月、遭三把牙刷、刷毛向外插入陰道不停旋轉、四肢被綁吊在兩張鐵架床上接受「懸空掛」酷刑、強迫體力勞動、坐老虎凳及電擊乳房和生殖器官等。<br />\n<br />\n杜斌當時表示，紀錄片透過12位勞教所親歷者回憶，講述她們曾遭受的酷刑，以事實戳穿遼寧當局指摘媒體造假的醜行。他向《蘋果》說：「就是要讓全世界都知道，在21世紀的中國，還有這種慘無人道的酷刑！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201218/ZVOWT4OSY5CDXJ5WD73KDCORJQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3ePSa2OlPyO-IsWHf-MdLv3GJGljKQ_iCX-Ah8gtTZJVDHHSvCFblbwjI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201218%2FZVOWT4OSY5CDXJ5WD73KDCORJQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3ePSa2OlPyO-IsWHf-MdLv3GJGljKQ_iCX-Ah8gtTZJVDHHSvCFblbwjI&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=26619f6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201218%2FZVOWT4OSY5CDXJ5WD73KDCORJQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3ePSa2OlPyO-IsWHf-MdLv3GJGljKQ_iCX-Ah8gtTZJVDHHSvCFblbwjI&h=0c1e8729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201218/ZVOWT4OSY5CDXJ5WD73KDCORJQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3ePSa2OlPyO-IsWHf-MdLv3GJGljKQ_iCX-Ah8gtTZJVDHHSvCFblbwjI</a><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\